LOADING

Insert your game disk and switch on the computer.  The game will now
load automatically.


CONTROLS

JOYSTICK:

                              ACCELERATE

                                 /\


    TURN/MOVE LEFT        <               >         TURN/MOVE RIGHT

                                 \/

                                BRAKE

FIRE BUTTON = Change Gear (High/Low)

KEYBOARD:

P = PAUSE
ESC = QUIT
S = SOUND FX

                   
HIGH SCORE NAME ENTRY

If you acheive a high score after playing you will be asked to enter
your mane.  Select the letters you require by moving the joystick left
or right to move the cursor and press fire to enter each letter.  When
you have entered your name move to "END" and press fire to end.

